    "Nevertheless, it is perhaps possible to make a comparison to the Catholic doctrine area of Christian Social Teaching (CST).",
    "This framework can be said to emphasize practical action in social justice, environmental stewardship, and the upholding of human dignity and individual virtues.",
    "The model's outputs, which focus on humility, temperance, truthfulness, and wisdom, alongside social responsibilities like environmental care and economic justice, are comparable to key principles of CST.",
